## Limitations

The exploration of gender roles is complex and multifaceted, with variations across different cultures and historical periods. This report primarily focuses on general theories and historical perspectives, which may not capture the full diversity of gender roles globally. Additionally, the sources used may have inherent biases based on their cultural and academic contexts. Further research could include more diverse cultural perspectives and contemporary studies on gender roles.